@startuml
actor Pembeli
participant View
participant Controller
participant PaymentGateway
participant Model
participant Database

Pembeli -> View : Menerima instruksi pembayaran
View --> Pembeli : Tampilkan instruksi

Pembeli -> PaymentGateway : Lakukan pembayaran via metode yang dipilih
PaymentGateway -> PaymentGateway : Proses transaksi

PaymentGateway -> Controller : POST /webhook/payment (callback data)
Controller -> Controller : Validasi signature & data

alt Pembayaran Sukses?
    Controller -> Model : update_status("Dibayar/Diproses") (Order & Payment)
    Model -> Database : update order & payment status
    Database --> Model : success
    Model --> Controller : success
    Controller -> Controller : Kirim notifikasi sukses ke Pembeli
    Controller -> Controller : Kirim notifikasi pesanan baru ke Penjual
else Tidak / Kadaluarsa
    Controller -> Model : update_status("Expired/Dibatalkan") (Order & Payment)
    Model -> Database : update order & payment status
    Database --> Model : success
    Model --> Controller : success
    Controller -> Controller : Kirim notifikasi gagal ke Pembeli
end

Controller --> PaymentGateway : HTTP 200 OK Response
@enduml
